glasses all the time and didn't have them on 
sometimes

18:30.980 --> 18:55.317
deeply religious man very very religious very 
heavily involved in the first magic church and

18:30.980 --> 18:55.317
pride and likewise his wife also uh very kind i 
suppose if i had a Mr. Heaton had many, many

